---
layout: layouts/dark.njk
permalink: "/corporate/terms/"
title: "Membership Terms"
description: "Contractual terms for the Prime Corporate Golf Club membership including usage, guest policy, and cancellation rules."
---
{% from "components/accordion.njk" import accordion %}
{% from "components/table.njk" import standard as renderTable %}
{% set transferFee = site.membership.transferFeeTHB | formatNumber %}
{% set annualRounds = site.membership.rounds %}
{% set guestPerSeat = site.membership.guestsPerSeat %}
{% set maxGuests = site.membership.maxGuests %}
{% set cancelHrs = site.membership.cancelHrs %}
<section class="container mt-8">
  <header class="mb-10">
    <span class="section-title">Membership Terms</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-2">Prime Corporate Golf Club</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300">Effective 20 October 2025. These terms apply to all active memberships unless superseded by a signed addendum.</p>
  </header>

  <nav class="card mb-8" aria-labelledby="terms-quick-reference">
    <h2 id="terms-quick-reference" class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Quick reference</h2>
    <ul class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-overview">Membership overview</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-scope">1. Membership scope</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-usage">2. Usage &amp; quota</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-guest">3. Guest policy</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-booking">4. Booking &amp; cancellation</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-conduct">5. Course conduct</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-fees">6. Fees &amp; payment</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-termination">7. Termination</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-law">8. Governing law</a></li>
      <li><a class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline hover:underline" href="#terms-contact">Concierge contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div id="terms-overview" class="table-wrap">
    {{ renderTable(
      ["Detail", "Description"],
      [
        ["Annual membership fee", "<strong>" ~ (site.membership.priceTHB | formatCurrencyTHB) ~ "</strong> plus VAT for a 12-month term."],
        ["Included usage", "<strong>" ~ annualRounds ~ " rounds</strong> per membership year. Green fee, caddy, and cart are included for each confirmed round."],
        ["Registered executives", "Two (2) named users employed by the member corporation."],
        ["Guest allowance", "Up to <strong>" ~ guestPerSeat ~ " guests</strong> per executive (maximum <strong>" ~ maxGuests ~ " guests</strong> when both executives attend)."],
        ["User transfer fee", "฿" ~ transferFee ~ " per change, subject to vetting."],
        ["Cancellation window", "Tee times must be amended or cancelled ≥ " ~ cancelHrs ~ " hours before play to avoid deduction."]
      ]
    ) }}
  </div>

  {% set termsAccordion = [
    {
      "title": "1. Membership scope",
      "id": "terms-scope",
      "content": "<p>The membership is corporate and may not be resold. Two named executives receive digital credentials and NFC cards. Additional corporate teams may request supplementary memberships subject to availability.</p><p>Replacement of a named executive requires written authorization and the ฿" ~ transferFee ~ " transfer fee. Replacement users must be direct employees or directors of the same corporate entity.</p>",
      "open": true
    },
    {
      "title": "2. Usage & quota",
      "id": "terms-usage",
      "content": "<p>The annual quota of <strong>" ~ annualRounds ~ " rounds</strong> is pooled at the corporate level. Each person (executive or guest) may consume one 18-hole round per day.</p><p>Unused rounds do not roll over. The concierge issues monthly statements summarizing rounds consumed, guest participation, and cancellations.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "3. Guest policy",
      "id": "terms-guest",
      "content": "<p>Guests must be accompanied by one of the registered executives at all times. One executive may host up to " ~ guestPerSeat ~ " guests (four-ball). When both executives play together they may host a party of up to " ~ maxGuests ~ " guests (eight golfers).</p><p>Executives are responsible for the conduct and dress code compliance of their guests.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "4. Booking & cancellation",
      "id": "terms-booking",
      "content": "<p>All tee times must be requested through the Prime concierge via phone, LINE OA, or email. Prime confirms within the published SLA.</p><p>Cancellations or amendments received less than " ~ cancelHrs ~ " hours before the scheduled tee time incur a deduction of one round per player. No-shows are charged the same deduction.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "5. Course conduct",
      "id": "terms-conduct",
      "content": "<p>Members and guests must follow partner course etiquette, pace of play, and caddy tipping policies. Prime reserves the right to suspend access for repeated violations.</p><p>Damage to course property is the responsibility of the member corporation. Prime is not liable for personal injury, loss, or property damage sustained during play.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "6. Fees & payment",
      "id": "terms-fees",
      "content": "<p>Invoices are denominated in Thai Baht and due within 30 days of issue. Late payments may lead to suspension until settled. Optional tournament, F&amp;B, or travel services are billed separately.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "7. Termination",
      "id": "terms-termination",
      "content": "<p>Prime may terminate the membership for breach of these terms, non-payment, fraud, or reputational risk. Unused rounds are forfeited upon termination.</p><p>The member corporation may request termination with 60 days’ notice. Refunds are not provided for early cancellation.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "8. Governing law",
      "id": "terms-law",
      "content": "<p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Kingdom of Thailand. Disputes shall be resolved by the Bangkok South Civil Court.</p>"
    }
  ] %}

  <div class="mt-10">
    {{ accordion(termsAccordion) }}
  </div>

  <section id="terms-contact" class="mt-12 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Concierge contact</h2>
    <p>Primary point of contact: <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.concierge }}" class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline">{{ site.contact.concierge }}</a> · <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phone | phoneHref }}" class="text-[var(--brand-gold)] no-underline">{{ site.contact.phone | formatPhone }}</a>.</p>
    <p>Physical correspondence should be addressed to {{ site.contact.address }}.</p>
  </section>
</section>
